headline: 4 Top Agriculture Operations Stocks Ready to Weather Near-Term Challenges
summary: The Agriculture - Operations industry is navigating volatile prices and rising costs, but innovation, exports and demand for sustainable food keep it resilient. CTVA, SMG, AVO and AGRO look promising.
